[
  {
    "text": "♪ Mellow instrumental hip-hop music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to \"Qualities of great AR experiences.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Alli Dryer, and I'm part of the Apple Design team ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "working on augmented reality.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "AR lets you deliver experiences that blend virtual objects ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the real world, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=21"
  },
  {
    "text": "creating the illusion that these objects actually exist.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "AR can be surprisingly immersive, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "and yet at the same time, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's always grounded in what's really happening.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "It allows you to visualize things ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "that would be impossible, risky, or hard to do ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=34"
  },
  {
    "text": "from a practical standpoint.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "Blurring the line between imagination and reality, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=39"
  },
  {
    "text": "an AR experience really feels like magic.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can completely transform people's surroundings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "through visuals and sound so they experience something new.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also add new layers of information to the environment ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=51"
  },
  {
    "text": "to enable quick and lightweight interactions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "Designing for augmented reality can be very different ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "from designing for 2D applications, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "but don't worry, we'll break it down here.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today I'm going to share criteria you can use ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "to decide if AR is right for the experience you're building, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "along with tips for handling some of the unique aspects ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "of augmented reality when you're designing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "your first AR experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "OK. So you're designing an app or feature ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "and wondering whether AR makes sense for you.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here are a few things to consider.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "AR can help you deliver a true representation of things.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "To show what I mean, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "let's look at an example of something AR does really well, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=91"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is to present the real-world size of an object.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "Say you're trying to educate people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "about how big a dinosaur is.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "You could just write it out, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "or show a picture, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "or you could unleash a virtual T. rex on the scene.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "In that case, there's no need to imagine ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=111"
  },
  {
    "text": "how big the dinosaur is.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "The AR experience gives the viewer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "an instant, visceral sense of scale ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "in a way that's truly immersive.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "This example comes from the app Monster Park, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "a game that lets people explore and control ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "the movement of animated three-dimensional dinosaurs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's fitting that the entire app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=129"
  },
  {
    "text": "revolves around this large-as-life AR experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "also emphasizing the creation of photos and videos for sharing.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "AR is at its most delightful when it affects and responds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "to what's immediately around you, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "involving physical space in a meaningful way.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "Say you're trying to design an app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "that helps with interior design, and you want to help people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "choose a paint color for their walls.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "You could use swatches or stock photography, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "but those aren't very accurate.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "Even better, you could show someone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=160"
  },
  {
    "text": "how their very own room would look ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "with freshly painted walls.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Color Snap app does just that.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "It allows people to choose a paint color ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then tap a wall to preview the effect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "Because it's AR, people can move around ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "to see how the new color will affect their space ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "from different vantage points.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=177"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, augmented reality allows you to create experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "that visualize virtual objects in 3D, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "which makes it easier to understand and evaluate them.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "With AR, you can build features that help people try on things ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "in a way that's virtual yet realistic enough ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "for someone to make a confident purchasing decision.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=195"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, the Warby Parker app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "lets people try on virtual glasses ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "so they can place an order knowing exactly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "how their frames will fit.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's faster to switch between frame styles in AR ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "than it would be to swap glasses in real life.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "Grounding virtual objects in the scene ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=211"
  },
  {
    "text": "is also really important.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "The quality of lighting and shadows in your experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "can have a huge impact on people's feeling ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "that things are really there, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "even when an object isn't very realistic.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "The IKEA Place app allows people to place ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=224"
  },
  {
    "text": "a piece of virtual furniture in their home ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "and get a more accurate sense ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "of what the updated room would look like.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=230"
  },
  {
    "text": "IKEA Place takes advantage of ARKit's built-in lighting ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "for realistic shadows that really settle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "the virtual furniture into the room.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "Visualizing in 3D can refer to objects, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "but don't forget about using people's surroundings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "as a canvas for your experiences.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can create new features with advanced visual effects, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "provide maps and 3D models that fit your brand, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "and even bring people's spaces into the game you're building ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "with iOS's new RoomPlan API.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "We've got a session on creating 3D room scans ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=260"
  },
  {
    "text": "that goes into detail about RoomPlan ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "if you want to learn more.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "AR lets you streamline actions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "by attaching digital capabilities to physical things, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "making your apps and features more efficient.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=271"
  },
  {
    "text": "You might have already experienced ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "how using the real world as input can speed things up ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=275"
  },
  {
    "text": "if you've ever scanned a code to order at a restaurant.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can use AR to build compact yet incredibly useful features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "that save people time.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS's Measure App, centering the camera on a person ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=287"
  },
  {
    "text": "automatically displays her height in just the right spot.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "The experience feels lightweight because there's very little UI, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "the interaction is based on device movement, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=298"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the measurement information disappears after you've seen it.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "This AR experience would be too limited to offer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "as an app on its own, but it really complements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "the other capabilities of the Measure app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, now you know you can use AR for your apps and features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=313"
  },
  {
    "text": "when you want to deliver a true representation, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "involve physical space in a meaningful way, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "visualize in 3D, and streamline actions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "by making use of what's in the environment.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=324"
  },
  {
    "text": "And as you can see, there are a lot of different ways ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=327"
  },
  {
    "text": "to incorporate AR into the experiences you're creating, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "whether it's as the main focus of the app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "or with a lighter hand as a feature that reduces friction.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=336"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, you've decided AR is right for your purposes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=339"
  },
  {
    "text": "and now it's time to get started with design.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=342"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you're designing for AR, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll need to consider some of the aspects ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "that make it different than traditional 2D interfaces.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=349"
  },
  {
    "text": "AR is spatial.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=353"
  },
  {
    "text": "AR is movement-based.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "And AR is tied to the physical environment.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll need to think about how to blend virtual elements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "into the scene, about ergonomics, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "and about working with a limited field of view.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now I'll go through tips you can keep in mind ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "when designing AR experiences.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=375"
  },
  {
    "text": "People using your app might be in places ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are difficult for AR, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "so what you can do to help is coach them ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=382"
  },
  {
    "text": "through different ways to get to a better experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=384"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Mission to Mars app does a great job ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=387"
  },
  {
    "text": "of getting people set up for success ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=389"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a strong coaching sequence.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a closer look at this example.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=393"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you're getting started, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "Mission to Mars highlights three different requirements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=398"
  },
  {
    "text": "you need in your environment to have a great session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=401"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, there's a reminder that AR can be immersive, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's wise to find a safe place to engage with it.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "This can be a particular concern ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "for experiences that involve wayfinding, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "where you'll need to take extra care ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "not to draw people's attention to the screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=415"
  },
  {
    "text": "for long periods of time.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=417"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, the app suggests that AR performs best ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=421"
  },
  {
    "text": "on surfaces with texture, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "rather than on glass or smooth white featureless planes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=425"
  },
  {
    "text": "LiDAR can help overcome ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "some of these challenging environmental conditions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=430"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you might be able to omit this suggestion ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=432"
  },
  {
    "text": "for some devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "And last, Mission to Mars advises people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=437"
  },
  {
    "text": "to find a bright space because AR works best ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "in environments that are properly lit.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=441"
  },
  {
    "text": "What's great about this coaching sequence is that it's quick, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=445"
  },
  {
    "text": "easy to navigate, and helps people understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to set up their environment for the best AR experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "The next tip is to take advantage of screen space.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'd be surprised how large a role it can play ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=456"
  },
  {
    "text": "in AR experience design.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=459"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, what is screen space? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=461"
  },
  {
    "text": "Think of screen space as a 2D layer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "that sits on top of the three-dimensional world ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "that's captured by your camera view.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=467"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's best to place text and interactive elements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "like buttons here in screen space, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=472"
  },
  {
    "text": "rather than in the 3D world of the camera ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=474"
  },
  {
    "text": "to preserve legibility.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=476"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's a great example from the Mission to Mars app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=478"
  },
  {
    "text": "that illustrates how to handle text in screen space.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "High-contrast text and buttons sit in a 2D screen space layer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=484"
  },
  {
    "text": "on top of the 3D scene below.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=488"
  },
  {
    "text": "The text updates as the camera moves to help you understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "how it relates to the 3D objects in the scene.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=494"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you do need to lock your text to something in the world, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=497"
  },
  {
    "text": "try to keep it billboarded or parallel to the screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=500"
  },
  {
    "text": "when possible.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "Focus on increasing contrast, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=504"
  },
  {
    "text": "bumping up type sizes and putting text on a background ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=506"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you can maintain accessibility.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "Design for constant movement.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=512"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's important that people understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=514"
  },
  {
    "text": "how and when to move their devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sometimes they'll need to move their bodies as well ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "in order to experience AR.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=520"
  },
  {
    "text": "Try to provide real-time feedback ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=523"
  },
  {
    "text": "with visual effects and sound as people move, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that even if the action is taking place out of view, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=527"
  },
  {
    "text": "people can still connect with the experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=530"
  },
  {
    "text": "Use simple, glanceable instructions and animations ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "to coach people how to move.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "It helps to place instructions in screen space ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=539"
  },
  {
    "text": "and to show them on an as-needed basis, rather than all up front.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's great to leverage the built-in coaching animations, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=545"
  },
  {
    "text": "but you can also create your own onboarding instructions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=548"
  },
  {
    "text": "that relate to your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "like this example from the app DoodleLens ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=552"
  },
  {
    "text": "that shows an iPhone panning back and forth ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=555"
  },
  {
    "text": "in front of a doodle.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=557"
  },
  {
    "text": "Ergonomic considerations are really important for AR.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=559"
  },
  {
    "text": "It can be exhausting to hold your arm out ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "for long periods of time, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "and uncomfortable to reach for buttons ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=567"
  },
  {
    "text": "that aren't positioned properly for one-handed use.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=569"
  },
  {
    "text": "Emphasize legibility at arm's length for the entire interface.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=573"
  },
  {
    "text": "Simplify interactions so that they can be completed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "with minimal effort.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "Use oversized buttons with high-contrast icons ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=581"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are easy to tap one-handed with a thumb.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=584"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's a nice example at the bottom of the screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=587"
  },
  {
    "text": "in DoodleLens.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=589"
  },
  {
    "text": "People are viewing AR experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=592"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a limited field of view ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "offered through a handheld device, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=595"
  },
  {
    "text": "so there's a good chance they might not be able to see ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "the full extent of something large.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=599"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's also a possibility that a virtual object ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=602"
  },
  {
    "text": "might be located out of view.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "Allow people to adjust the scale of an object, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=607"
  },
  {
    "text": "in case they're not able to back up far enough ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=610"
  },
  {
    "text": "to see the whole thing.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=612"
  },
  {
    "text": "This example from AR Quick Look ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=614"
  },
  {
    "text": "uses a pinch gesture for direct manipulation.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's also a haptic so that you can feel it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=620"
  },
  {
    "text": "when you scale something past 100 percent.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=622"
  },
  {
    "text": "When something is out of view to the right or to the left, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=626"
  },
  {
    "text": "use sounds and haptics and provide simple indicators ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=629"
  },
  {
    "text": "or text instructions in screen space.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=632"
  },
  {
    "text": "It can also be helpful to provide a map ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=635"
  },
  {
    "text": "or bird's-eye view showing someone's orientation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=637"
  },
  {
    "text": "and illustrating that the object is located ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=640"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the opposite direction.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=642"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example from the RoomPlan experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "the small 3D model drawing at the bottom of the view ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=647"
  },
  {
    "text": "helps you preview your results ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=649"
  },
  {
    "text": "and keep track of what has been scanned so far.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=651"
  },
  {
    "text": "It can be difficult for people peering through a screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=655"
  },
  {
    "text": "to understand the location of virtual objects in space ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=657"
  },
  {
    "text": "unless they're behaving realistically.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=660"
  },
  {
    "text": "Depth cues that help people see how far away things are ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=663"
  },
  {
    "text": "can help with this.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=666"
  },
  {
    "text": "The size of objects, perspective effects ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=667"
  },
  {
    "text": "like diminishing towards the horizon, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=670"
  },
  {
    "text": "realistic shadows and lighting, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=672"
  },
  {
    "text": "the proper amount of detail in your textures, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=674"
  },
  {
    "text": "and overlapping objects create a feeling of depth ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=676"
  },
  {
    "text": "and help people perceive spatial relationships.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=679"
  },
  {
    "text": "I want to highlight one depth cue that's tricky to work with ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=682"
  },
  {
    "text": "but can really help people understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=685"
  },
  {
    "text": "where things are located relative to each other: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=687"
  },
  {
    "text": "overlapping, also known as occlusion.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=690"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's an example of overlapping you can see in AR Quick Look.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=693"
  },
  {
    "text": "The virtual airplane seems like it's positioned ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=697"
  },
  {
    "text": "behind the wooden blocks on the desk ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=699"
  },
  {
    "text": "because the lower part of it is hidden.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=701"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, craft experiences that last ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=704"
  },
  {
    "text": "no more than a minute or two.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=706"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is for the ergonomic reasons I mentioned earlier, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=708"
  },
  {
    "text": "but also because AR is a resource-intensive superpower ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=711"
  },
  {
    "text": "that has a big impact on battery and thermals.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=715"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you do end up creating a longer experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=719"
  },
  {
    "text": "make sure that you build in breaks.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=722"
  },
  {
    "text": "For All Mankind: Time Capsule is an AR experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=724"
  },
  {
    "text": "that allows you to explore the For All Mankind universe.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=727"
  },
  {
    "text": "The app complements the TV show, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=730"
  },
  {
    "text": "telling stories through interactive objects.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=732"
  },
  {
    "text": "Time Capsule is presented in chapters ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=735"
  },
  {
    "text": "that provide moments of rest ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=737"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a place to pause then return to the experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=739"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today I shared tips to help overcome some of the challenges ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=743"
  },
  {
    "text": "with working on AR features.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=746"
  },
  {
    "text": "You've learned to guide people to the right environment, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=748"
  },
  {
    "text": "to take advantage of screen space, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=751"
  },
  {
    "text": "to design for constant movement, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=753"
  },
  {
    "text": "to think about ergonomics and a limited field of view, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=755"
  },
  {
    "text": "to use depth cues, and to limit the duration of the experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=758"
  },
  {
    "text": "to keep people from getting fatigued.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=761"
  },
  {
    "text": "Augmented Reality feels like magic when it's useful, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=763"
  },
  {
    "text": "delightful, and relates to the physical world.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=766"
  },
  {
    "text": "AR allows you to see virtual objects ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=769"
  },
  {
    "text": "or even to transform your environment.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=771"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can attach digital capabilities to physical things ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=774"
  },
  {
    "text": "to create a layer of useful information and actions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=777"
  },
  {
    "text": "The AR features and apps that you create ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=780"
  },
  {
    "text": "will transform how people work, learn, play, shop, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=782"
  },
  {
    "text": "and connect with the world.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10131/?time=785"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't wait to see what you'll build next ",
